| 5 | No input validation pattern | 🟡 Medium | Injection prevention |
| 6 | No CORS configuration | 🟡 Medium | Access control |
| 7 | No 404 handler | 🟡 Medium | Info disclosure |
| 8 | Hardcoded port | 🟢 Minor | Configuration |
| 9 | No graceful shutdown | 🟢 Minor | Reliability |
