| Category | Issue | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| **Security Headers** | None present | Added `helmet()` |
| **Rate Limiting** | No DoS protection | Added `express-rate-limit` |
| **CORS** | Implicit policy | Explicit `cors()` with allowed origin |
| **Body Parsing** | Missing | `express.json()` with 10kb size limit |
| **Input Validation** | None | `express-validator` on query params |
| **Error Handling** | No global handler | 404 catch-all + global error middleware |
| **Data Leakage** | Emails exposed unconditionally | Strip sensitive fields from responses |
| **Fingerprinting** | `X-Powered-By` header exposed | `app.disable('x-powered-by')` |
| **Configuration** | Hardcoded port | Read from `process.env.PORT` |
| **Stack Trace Leak** | Default Express errors expose internals | Production-safe error messages |

